title: Panko-Topped Shrimp with Broccoli, Buttery Green Pea Rice and Lemony Mayo
description: Crunchy, golden breadcrumbs make this easy baked shrimp a fast family favourite! Our DIY lemony mayo is great dolloped onto the shrimp and served as a dipper for broccoli.
